com.davidjarski.vfatreader

Class Directory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.davidjarski.vfatreader.Directory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<DirectoryEntry>

    public class Directory
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<DirectoryEntry>
    A Directory is a iterable list of DirectoryEntries.

    A factory method is provided to get the root directory of a Disk.
    The root directory is currently the only directory supported by this class.
    Author:
    David Jarski (c) 2014-07-31
